data.description: Seller has put a new roof on September 2023. This Generous Brick and Vinyl split is situated on a corner level lot in the heart of Vienna.  Owner has put in newer flooring and updated bath, plus a few other updates. Lots of room in lower level. The lower level rec room features a brick faced fireplace. Additional rooms include a full bath, Library/Study and 16 x 13 Utility Room. The "other room" noted in the lower level, is accessible from the inside or the outside, offering a great space for crafting or workshop. Enjoy the 23 x 10 screened porch. Vinyl sided 32 x 26 detached garage offers many opportunities. Measurements are rounded.
